'''''Alai Payum Nenjangal''''' is a [[1983 in film|1983]] [[Tamil language|Tamil]]  [[Cinema of India|Indian]] [[feature film]] [[Film director|directed]] by H.Ramesh for D & PG Producations. It stars newcomers in the lead roles.<ref>{{cite web|title=Alai Payum Nenjangal Vinyl LP Records|url=http://musicalaya.net/imgviewer.php?mod=lpcovers/37/3/1/1|publisher=musicalaya|accessdate=2014-04-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140424014825/http://musicalaya.net/imgviewer.php?mod=lpcovers%2F37%2F3%2F1%2F1|archive-date=24 April 2014|dead-url=yes|df=dmy-all}}</ref>

